{
  "stem": "9168.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that's kind of how-- Who was your immediate supervisor when you first arrived?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I first arrived, I-- my immediate-- immediate-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I reported to a woman, as I remember first, Captain Sara Kruskell, S-A-R-A K-R-U-S-K-A-L-L, a-- a WAC captain.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my immediate court reporting supervisor was the Chief of Reporters, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Charles Foster, of somewhere in northern California.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure that we were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I do not remember specifically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I had to become aware of the fact that we were subject to military control.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to follow military orders, and when they were given-- such as you will not go out on the street and walk around Nuremberg after-- you will not, after 7:00 at night, especially, when it was getting dark.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was aware that-- I was told that we were going to be a team of about six reporters on the Doctors' Trial.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was told I was going to work the Doctors' Trial.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the most important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the trial I wanted above all trials.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because the-- Goering and all of the major Nazi leaders were what I called the political animals.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the doctors were the scientists, the educated scientists, who had taken the Hippocratic oath to heal and cure.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had learned by that time enough of what was going on in these camps, somehow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm sure that we-- there was-- that there were orientation sessions for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure they involved some kind of film that the US Army had us attend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember specifically.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was to be part of the court reporting team.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were assigned to a large office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other trial had ended.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
